		"description": "Right now, the only way to have a SearchView in the ActionBar is to also have it tied to the search on a TableView. I need to be able to do remote API searches via a SearchView in the ActionBar.\r\n\r\nPerhaps now is the time to tweak TableView.search to fire a search event instead of only filtering? This would allow us to accomplish the same thing, right? Even better, that would allow for some great UI even if the data is remote.",
